---
import { CldImage } from "astro-cloudinary";

---

<section class="bg-black py-10 lg:py-16 relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border-soft">
  <div class="motion-drift absolute -left-10 bottom-0 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-wine/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="motion-drift absolute right-0 top-10 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-off-white/6 blur-3xl" style="--float-delay: 1.2s"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[0.88fr_1.12fr] gap-8 lg:gap-14 items-center">
    <div data-reveal="blur" class="flex flex-col gap-5">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gold">
        <span class="h-px w-10 bg-gold"></span>
        Behind the shine
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-text-primary font-bold text-h2">
        Premium results start with how we work when nobody is watching.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        We founded Duartes Auto Detailing to give busy Bay Area owners a premium answer to car care without sacrificing time, trust, or finish quality. That means operational discipline, respectful service at your location, and a standard that feels just as strong in the process as it does in the result.
      </p>
      <div data-reveal="scale" style="--reveal-delay: 180ms" class="motion-card-hover relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-wine-soft/20 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(110,43,44,0.16),rgba(23,24,27,0.96))] px-6 py-6 shadow-lg">
        <div class="motion-sheen"></div>
        <p class="text-wine-tint font-medium italic leading-relaxed">
          "When you book with us, you are booking consistency, trust, and a finish that looks intentional from every angle."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-reveal="scale" class="relative">
      <div class="motion-float-slow overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/8 shadow-lg">
        <CldImage
          src="about-team_aexfzl"
          alt="Technician at Duartes Auto Detailing"
          width={1280}
          height={900}
          sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 56vw"
          class="w-full object-cover object-left min-h-96 lg:min-h-136"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/46 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="motion-enter absolute left-5 bottom-5 rounded-xl border border-wine-soft/18 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(15,16,18,0.62),rgba(79,29,30,0.36))] px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-md" style="--enter-delay: 260ms">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-gold">Bay Area mobile specialists</p>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Professional-grade service, brought directly to your home, office, or private garage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
